<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٥٢٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٦٥٦٦ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ قَالَ:</span> قُلْتُ لِعَطَاءٍ: الصَّلَاةُ عَلَى الْجِنَازَةِ فِي الْحِينِ الَّذِي تُكْرَهُ فِيهِ الصَّلَاةُ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«تُكْرَهُ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>